hadiths[193]{hadithnumber,text}:
3198,Hazrat Ata sey riwayat hai ke hum Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) key janaazey mein sarf key maqam par hazir huye. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : ye Hazrat Memuna hain. jab tum unka janaza uthao to usey (behangam) harkat na dena aur na usey ziyada uper nichey karna. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key nikah mein ( wafat key waqt ) no biwiyan thin. aap aath key liye baari muqarrar farmatey they aur eik key liye baari muqarrar na farmatey they.
3199,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut huye to aap key nikah mein no biwiyan thin. aap un sab key paas shab basri farmatey they, ilawa Hazrat sauda (Raziallahu anha) key ke unhoney apni baari ka din raat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key liye hiba farma diya tha."
3200,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik raat mein apni sab aurton key paas ghoom aatey they jab ke un dino aap ki no biwiyan thin.
3201,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mujhey un aurton par ghussa aata tha jo apney aap ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (sey nikah) key liye khud pesh karti thin. main kehti thi : koi azad aurat bhi (mard sey shaadi karney key liye) apney aap ko khud pesh kar sakti hai? to Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaari : (تُرْجِیْ مَنْ تَشَآءُ …),""aap apni jis biwi ko chahen door rakhen aur jis ko chahen apney qarib kar lein. mainey kaha : Allah ki qism ! main to samajhti hun ke aap ka Rab taala bhi aap ki khahish aur pasand ko pura karney mein jaldi karta hai.''"
3202,"Hazrat Sahal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik dafa main sahaba mein betha tha ke eik aurat aa kar kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! main aap sey nikah key liye apney aap ko pesh karti hun. aap merey barey mein faisla karen. (aap khamosh rahey to) eik aadmi khada huwa aur kehney laga : (agar aap ko zarurat nahin to) mujh sey us ka nikah kar dijiye. aap ney farmaya : ja koi chiz talash kar key la, agar-che lohey ki anguthi hi ho (taake mehar mein dey sakey ). wo shakhs gaya magar usey koi chiz na mili yahan tak ke lohey ki anguthi bhi na mili. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tujhey Quran Majeed ki kuch suraten yad hain? us ney kaha : haan. aap ney Quran Majeed ki un Suraton (ki taaleem) key iwaz us ka us aurat sey nikah farma diya."
3203,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney khabar di ke jab Allah Taala ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya ke aap apni biwiyon ko (Talaq leney ka) ikhtiyar den to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (sab sey pehley) merey paas aaye aur farmaya : Aaisha ! main tujh sey eik baat zikr karta hun. to us (ka jawab deney) key barey mein jaldi na karna yahan tak ke apney waliden sey mashwara kar ley. kyonkey aap jantey they ke merey waliden kabhi bhi aap sey judai ka mashwara nahin dey saktey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (ye aayat padhi) « { یَآیُّھَا النَّبِیُّ قُلْ لِّاَزْوَاجِکَ … } » aey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! apni biwiyon sey keh dijiye ki agar tum duniya ki zindagi aur uski zeenat ki talabgar ho to aao main tumhen kuch saman dey kar farigh kar dun … . mainey kaha : main us barey mein apney waliden sey mashwara talab karun ? bila shak o shubha main to Allah taalaa, uskey Rasool aur aakhirat ki talabgar hun."
3204,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni biwiyon ko Talaq ka ikhtiyar diya tha to kya ye Talaq ho qaee?
3205,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen Talaq ka ikhtiyar diya tha magar hum sab ney aap ko tarjeeh di, lihaza ye ikhtiyar dena Talaq nahin bana."
3206,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat sey pehley aap ko mazeed aurton sey nikah karney ki ijazat dey di gaee thi.
3207,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala ko piyarey huye to is sey pehley aap ko rukhsat dey di gaee thi ke aap jis aurat sey chahen, nikah farmaeyn."
3208,"Hazrat Alqama sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key sath tha aur wo Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key paas they. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kuch jawaanon key paas tashrif laye … Imam Nasai ney kaha : jis tarah main chahta hun is tarah main (apney ustaad sey) lafz « فِتْییَۃً » ( jawaanon ) nahin samajh saka … aur farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs wusat rakhta ho, wo zarur nikah karey kyonkey nikah nazar ko neecha aur sharmgah ko mehfooz kar deta hai. aur jis shakhs key paas nikah ki wusat na ho (woh rozey rakha karey kyonkey) roza rakhna uski shehwat ko kuchal dega."
3209,"Hazrat Alqama sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : kya aap pasand farmaeyngey ke main eik nojawan ladki sey aap ki shaadi kar dun? to Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney Alqama ko (yani mujhey) bula liya, phir bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (nojawanon sey) farmaya tha : tum mein sey jo shakhs nikah ki taqat rakhey, wo nikah karey kyonkey nikah nazar ko ziyada jhuka deney wala aur sharmgah ko ziyada mehfooz kar deney wala hai. aur jo shakhs nikah ki taqat na rakhey, wo rozey rakha karey kyonkey roza uski shehwat ko kuchal dega."
3210,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey ( jab hum jawan they ) farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs nikah ki istataat rakhey, wo nikah karey aur jo istataat na rakhey, wo rozey rakhey kyonkey rozey rakhna uski shehwat ko kuchalney ka zaria hai. abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke is hadees ki sanad mein Aswad ka zikr sahih nahin. (Alqama ka zikr sahih hai jaisa ke sabiqa riwayaat mein hai.)"
3211,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey farmaya : aey nojawan logo ! tum mein sey jo shakhs nikah ki taqat rakhey, wo shaadi karey kyonkey ye nazar ko ziyada jhuka deney wala aur sharmgah ko ziyada mehfooz kar deney wala hai. aur jo shakhs taqat na rakhey to wo rozey rakha kerey. bilashuba roza uski shehwat ko kuchal dega."
3212,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey farmaya : aey nojawan logo! tum mein sey jo shakhs nikah ki taqat rakhey, wo shadi kar ley. aur (raawi ney) puri hadees bayan ki."
3213,"Hazrat Alqama sey riwayat hai ke main Mina mein Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key sath chal raha tha ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) unhen miley aur khadey ho kar un sey baaten karney lagey. kehney lagey : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman! kya main kisi nojawan ladki sey aapki shaadi na karun? shayad wo aap ko aapki guzishta jawani ki yad dila dey. Hazrat Abdullah farmaney lagey : agar aap ney ye baat farmaai hai to baja farmaya hai kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen farmaya tha : aey nojawan logo! jo tum mein sey nikah ki taqat rakhey, wo nikah kerey."
3214,Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ko tarake-nikah ki ijazat na di. agar aap unhen ijazat detey to hum khassi ho jatey.
3215,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tarake-nikah sey mana farmaya.
3216,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tarake-nikah sey mana farmaya. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke Qatada Ash-as sey badey Hafiz aur ziyada qabile-bharosa hain, magar (yahan ) Ash-as ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai. «wallahu taala aalam»."
3217,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main nojawan aadmi hun. mujhey apney barey mein khadsha hai ke kahin mujh sey bad-kari na ho jaey, jab ke mujh mein itni wusat nahin ke nikah kar sakun. to kya main khassi ho jaaun? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney munh mod liya yahan tak ke mainey teen dafa ye baat kahi. aakhir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Abu-Hurera ! jo kuch tu ney karna hai qalam Ilaahi wo likh kar khushk ho chuka. ab chahey to khassi ho ya na ho. Imam abu Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) farmatey hain : Auzai ney ye hadees Zohri sey nahin suni. lekin ye hadees sahih hai. usey Yunus ney Zohri sey riwayat kya hai."
3218,Hazrat Saad bin Hisham sey riwayat hai ke main ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. mainey kaha : main aap sey tarake-nikah ka masla poochhna chahta hun. uskey barey mein aapka kya khayal hai? wo farmaney lagin : aisey na kar. kya tu ney Allah Taala ka farman nahin suna : « { وَلَقَدْ اَرْسَلْنَا رُسُلاً … }  (aey Nabi ! ) hamney aap sey pehley bahut sey Rasool bhejey. un sab ki biwiyan aur aulad thi. lihaza tarake-nikah na kar.
3219,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke chand as-haab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (ikhattey huye un) main sey eik ney kaha : main aurton sey shaadi nahin karunga. dusrey ney kaha : main gosht nahin khaunga. teesrey ney kaha : main bistar par nahin sounga. chauthey ney kaha : main rozey rakhunga, kabhi nikah nahin karunga. ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunchi to aap ney Allah Taala ki hamd o sana bayan farmaai, phir farmaya : kya haal hai un logon ka jo aisi aisi baaten kehtey hain. halanke mein (nafl) namaz bhi padhta hun aur sota bhi hun. (nafl) rozey bhi rakhta hun aur nikah bhi karta hun aur mainey (eik sey zayed) aurton sey shaadi bhi kar rakhi hai, lihaza jo shakhs meri sunnat aur tareeq kaar ko napasand kerega, us ka mujh sey koi talluq nahin."
3220,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen shakhs aisey hain ke Allah Taala ney un ki madad karney ka zimma ley rakha hai : wo ghulam jo apni azadi ka muahida karey aur uski niyat raqam ada karney ki ho. aur wo shakhs jo gunah sey bachney (paakbaazi) ki niyat sey nikah kerey. aur jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad kerey.
3221,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey shaadi ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. aap ney farmaya : Jabir ! shaadi ki hai? mainey kaha : haan. aap ney farmaya : kanwari sey ya bewa sey? mainey kaha : bewa sey. aap ney farmaya : kanwari sey kyon na shaadi ki. to us sey dil lagi karta, wo tujh sey dil lagi karti."
3222,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey miley aur kehney lagey : Jabir! tu ney merey baad ( meri adam mojudgi mein) shaadi kar li hai? mainey kaha : ji han, aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : kanwari sey shaadi ki hai ya bewa sey? mainey kaha : bewa sey. aap ney farmaya : kanwari sey kyon na shaadi ki. wo tujh sey ji bhar kar piyaar karti."
3223,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko nikah ka pegham bheja. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo (tumharey muqabley mein) chhoti hai. phir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney pegham bheja to aap ney un sey Fatima ka nikah kar diya.
3224,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Usman ney Marwan key daure-hukoomat mein, jab ke wo nojawan they, Saeed bin Zaid ki beti, jiski walida binte-Qais thin, ko bitta Talaq dey di. us ladki ki khaala Hazrat Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu anha) ney usey pegham bheja ke wo Abdullah bin Amr ( khawind ) key ghar sey muntaqil ho jaey. Marwan ney ye suna to Saeed ki beti ko pegham bheja aur hukm diya ke wo apney khawind key ghar wapis jaey. aur us sey puchha ke wo apney asal ghar mein iddat mukammal karney sey pehley kyon muntaqil hui? to usney wapsi pegham bheja aur bataya ke meri khaala (sahabiya) ney mujhey hukm diya tha. (Marwan ney unhen pegham bheja to) Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha ke main abu-Amr bin Hafs (Raziallahu anhu) key nikah mein thi. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib ko Yamen ka ameer muqarrar farmaya to mera khawind bhi unkey sath gaya aur wahan sey mujhey aakhiri Talaq jo (teen talaaqon mein sey) baqi thi, bhej di aur mera kharch deney key liye Hazrat Haris bin Hisham aur Ayash bin abi Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) ko keh diya. mainey Haris aur ayaash ko pegham bheja ke mujhey mera kharch bhejein jiska merey khawind ney hukm diya hai. wo kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! tera hamarey zimmey koi kharch nahin magar ye ke to hamila ho. aur to hamari ijazat key baghair hamari rihaaish-gaah mein bhi nahin reh sakti. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaee aur aap sey pura maamla zikr kya. aap ney un (key mauqif) ki tasdeeq farmaai. mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! to main kahan rahun? aap ney farmaya : to Abdullah bin Umme-Maktum na-bina key ghar muntaqil ho ja, jis ka Allah Taala ney apni kitab mein tazkira farmaya hai. mainey unkey yahan iddat guzari. unki nazar khatam ho chuki thi. main wahan (bila khatkey) apney kapdey utaar sakti thi. yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mera nikah Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey farma diya. Marwan ney unki is baat ko taslim na kya aur kaha : mainey ye baat tujh sey pehley kisi sey nahin suni. main to usi tareeq par amal karunga jis par mainey pehley logon ko paya. ye riwayat (is jagah) mukhtasar ( bayan hui ) hai."
3225,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat abu-Huzaifa bin Utba bin Rabeea bin Abd Shams (Raziallahu anhu) jo ghazwa Badr mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath hazir huye they, ney Hazrat Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ko mutbanna ( munh bola ) beta bana liya tha aur unka nikah apni bhatiji hind bint waleed bin Utba bin Rabeea bin Abd Shams sey kar diya tha, halanke Hazrat Salim eik Ansari aurat key azad karda ghulam they, jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Zaid ko mutbanna (munh bola) beta bana liya tha. aur jahiliyat mein ye dastur tha ke jab koi shakhs kisi ko beta bana leta to log usko usi ka beta kehtey. wo uska waris bhi banta tha yahan tak ke Allah Taala ney us barey mein ye aayat utaari : « { اُدْعُوْھُمْ لِاٰبَآئِھِمْ ھُوَ … } » un ( متبناؤں ) ko unkey asli baapon ki taraf mansub karo. Allah Taala key nazdik ye baat ziyada qarin insaf hai. albatta agar tum unkey asli baapon ko na jantey ho to unhen apna bhai ya Mola kaho. lihaza jis (mutbanna) ka baap malum na ho, wo ( beta bananey waley ka) Mola ya deeni bhai hoga. (ye hadees is jagah) mukhtasar ( bayan hui ) hai."
3226,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki do pak biviyon Hazrat Aaisha aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Hazrat abu-Huzaifa bin Utba bin Rabeea bin Abd Shams (Raziallahu anhu) jo jange-Badar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath hazir huye they, ney Hazrat Salim (Raziallahu anhu) jo Ansaar ki eik aurat key azad karda ghulam they, ko beta bana liya tha, jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) ko beta banaya tha, neez Hazrat abu-Huzaifa bin Utba ney Hazrat Salim ka nikah apni sagi bhatiji hind bint waleed bin Utba bin Rabeea sey kar diya tha. aur Hazrat Hind bint waleed bin Utba (Raziallahu anha) awwaleen muhajrin mein sey thin aur wo un dino Quraish ki bewa khawatin mein sey afzal khatoon thin. jab Allah Taala ney Hazrat Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) key barey mein ye aayat utaari : « { اُدْعُوْھُمْ لِاٰبَائِھِمْ ھُوَ اَقْسَطُ عِنْدَاللّٰہ } » mutbannaon mein sey har eik ko uskey asli baap ki taraf mansub kya gaya. agar uskey baap ka pata na chal saka to usey mutbanna bananey walon ka maula kaha gaya."
3227,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : duniya walon key nazdik hasab sirf maal ka naam hai jiska wo khayal rakhtey hain. (rishtedari waghera key waqt).
3228,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur main eik aurat sey nikah kya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey miley aur farmaya : Jabir ! tu ney shaadi kar li hai? mainey kaha : ji haan. farmaya : kanwari sey ya bewa sey? mainey arz kya : bewa sey. aap ney farmaya : tu ney kanwari sey kyon na shaadi ki ? wo tujh sey dil lagi karti. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! meri kaee behnein hain. mainey khadsha mehsus kya ke kanwari aurat merey aur unkey darmiyan rukawat na ban jaey. aap ney farmaya : phir theek hai. aurat sey uskey Deen ki wajeh sey nikah kya jata hai ya maal o jamaal ki wajeh sey. to Deen wali aurat ko pasand kar. terey haath khaak aalud hon.
3229,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : mujhey eik khandani aur martabey wali aurat mili hai magar wo baanjh hai. to kya main us sey shaadi kar lun? aap ney usey mana farma diya, phir wo dobara aap key paas aaya to aap ney phir mana farmaya, phir wo teesri baar aaya. to aap ney phir rok diya. tab aap ney farmaya : aisi aurton sey shaadi karo jo ziyada bachey janne wali, khub mohabbat karney wali hon. yaqinan main tumhari kasrat ki wajeh sey fakhr karunga."
3230,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada ( Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Marsad bin abi Marsad Ghanwi (Raziallahu anhu) bahut bahadur aur qawi shakhs they. wo Makka Mukarrama sey musalman qaidi utha kar Madina ley aatey they. unhoney farmaya : mainey eik musalman qaidi sey tey kya ke main tumhen utha kar ley jaaunga. Makka main eik bad-kar aurat rehti thi jiska naam Unaq tha. wo (daure-jahiliyat mein) mujh sey dostana talluqaat rakhti thi. (us din) wo nikli to usney eik deewar key saye mein mujhey khada dekha. kehney lagi : kon! Marsad hai? khush aamadid aur marhabaa ho aey Marsad! aao ghar chalen, raat hamarey paas theherna. mainey kaha : aey Unaq! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zina ko haram qarar diya hai. us ney shor macha diya : aey khemon mein rehney walo! ye wo pith ka kanta hai jo tumharey qaidi Makka sey utha kar Madina ley jata hai. mein Khandama pahad ki taraf bhag nikla (aur eik ghaar mein ja chupa). aath aadmi merey peechey bhagey. wo aa kar (aen us ghaar key oopper) merey sar ki seedh mein khadey ho gaey aur peshab karney lagey. yahan tak ke unka peshab merey ooper girta tha. lekin Allah Taala ney unhen mujh sey andha kar diya (aur wo nakam wapis chaley gaey.) main phir apney us sathi key paas pahuncha aur usey uthaya. jab main usey utha kar peelu key darakhton key jhund key paas pahuncha to mainey uski bediyan todin. phir main usey ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa gaya. mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main Unaq sey nikah kar lun? aap khamosh rahey, phir ye aayat utri : « { وَالزَّانِیَۃُ لاَیَنْکِحُھَآ اِلاَّ زَانٍ … } » zaani aurat sey zaani mard ya mushrik hi nikah karta hai. aap ney mujhey bulaya, ye aayat merey samney tilawat farmaey, aur farmaya : to us sey nikah mat kar."
3231,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : merey nikah main eik aurat hai jo mujhey sab logon sey ziyada piyari hai magar wo kisi chhed chhaad karney waley ko nahin rokti. aap ney farmaya : usey Talaq dey dey. wo kehney laga : main us sey sabr nahin kar sakta. aap ney farmaya : phir isi tarah faeyda uthata reh. abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees sahih nahin hai kyonkey Abdul-Karim (raawi) qawi nahin hai, jabkey Harun bin Riaab us sey ziyada behtar hai. aur us ney us hadees ko mursal bayan kya hai. chunkey Harun qabile-bharosa hai, lihaza abdul-kareem key bajaey uski hadees sahih kehlaney key ziyada laaiq hai."
3232,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurton sey chaar wujuhat ki bina par nikah kya jata hai : maal ki bana par, hasab o nasab ki bina par, khoobsurti ki bana par. to Deen wali ko hasil kar, terey haath khaak aalud hun."
3233,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya : kon-si aurat behtar hai? aap ney farmaya : wo aurat ke jab khawind usey dekhey to wo usey khush kar dey. aur jab usey koi hukm dey to wo uski itaat karey aur apney nafs aur maal mein uski mukhalifat na karey jisey wo napasand karta ho."
3234,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : duniya sab ki sab waqti faaedey ki chiz hai. aur duniya key saman mein sey behtareen chiz nek aurat hai.
3235,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap Ansari aurton mein sey kisi key sath shaadi nahin farmaeyngey? aap ney farmaya : un mein ghairat bahut hai.
3236,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aadmi ney eik Ansari aurat ko shaadi ka pegham bheja. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tu ney usey dekha hai? usney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya, (pehley) usey dekh ley."
3237,Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur main eik aurat ko shaadi ka pegham bheja. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tu ney usey dekha hai? mainey kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : usey dekh ley. is tareeqey sey tumharey darmiyan mohabbat o ulfat paida hona ziyada mumkin hoga.
3238,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey shawwaal mein nikah farmaya. aur shawwaal hi mein mujhey aap ney ghar basaya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) pasand farmati thin ke unki rishtedar aurton ki rukhsati shawwal mein ho. (aap farmati thin : ) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwiyon mein sey kon mujh sey badh kar aap key yahan khush nasib sabit hui?
3239,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai jo ke awwalin muhaajir aurton mein sey thin, kehti hain : mujhey Abdur-Rehman bin Auf aur chand dusrey sahaba ney shaadi ka pegham bheja lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey apney azad karda ghulam Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) key liye talab farma liya. aur is sey pehley main ye sun chuki thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs mujh sey mohabbat rakhta hai, wo Usama sey mohabbat rakhey. chunanche jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey is barey mein baat farmaai to mainey arz kya : merey barey mein aap ko kulli ikhtiyar hasil hai. aap jis sey pasand farmaeyn, mera nikah farma den. aap ney farmaya : tum Umme-Sharik (Raziallahu anha) key ghar chali jaao. Hazrat Umme-Sharik (Raziallahu anha) maal daar Ansari khatoon thin aur Allah Taala key raastey mein bahut kuch kharch kya karti thin. unkey yahan ( bahut ) mehman aaya kartey they. mainey kaha : theek hai. mein chali jaaungi. phir aap ney farmaya : to aisey na karna kyonkey Umme-Shareek key ghar to aksar mehman aatey rehtey hain. mujhey ye baat napasand hai ke terey sar sey odhni sarak jaey ya teri pindliyon sey kapda hat jaey, phir log tujhey ( khuley badan) dekhengey to tujhey ye napasand hoga, is liye to apney chacha zaad bhai Abdullah bin Amr bin Umme-Maktoom key ghar muntaqil ho ja. aur wo bani Fahar qabiley sey talluq rakhtey hain. main unkey yahan muntaqil ho gaee. riwayat mukhtasar hai."
3240,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs kisi dusrey key pegham nikah par apna pegham nikah na bhejey.
3241,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dhoka dahi key liye bhaw na badhao, koi shehri kisi dehati ka saman na bechey. koi shakhs apney bhai key sodey par soda na karey aur na apney bhai key pegham nikah par apna pegham bhejey. aur na koi aurat apni saukan ki Talaq ka mutalba karey ke uskey bartan mein jo hai usey ulta dey (usey hasil honey waley faeydon sey mehrum kar dey )."
3242,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs apney (deeni) bhai key peghame-nikah par apna pegham na bhejey.
3243,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs apney bhai key pegham nikah par apna pegham na bhejey yahan tak ke wo nikah kar ley ya pegham chhod dey.
3244,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs apney kisi ( deeni ) bhai key pegham nikah par apna pegham na bhejey.
3245,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke tum mein sey koi shakhs kisi dusrey key sodey par soda karey ya uskey pegham nikah par pegham bhejey, yahan tak ke pehley pegham bhejney wala irada tarak kar dey ya dusrey ko ijazat de-dey."
3246,"Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman aur Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Soban sey riwayat hai ke un dono ney Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey unkey mamley key mutalliq puchha to Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mujhey merey khawind ney teen talaaqen dey den. aur mujhey khaney peeney key liye nakaafi kharcha bheja. mainey kaha : agar to rihaaish aur khaney peeney ka kharcha mera haq banta hai to Allah ki qism ! main pura pura kharcha talab karungi, ye maamuli sa ghalla nahin lungi. (merey khawind key) wakeel ney kaha : terey liye (qanooni taur par) rihaaish ya nafqa (kharcha) nahin hai. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaee aur aap sey ye baat zikr ki. aap ney farmaya : terey liye (dorane-iddat mein) rihaaish aur kharcha nahin hai. to falan aurat (Umme-Sharik) key yahan iddat guzar ley. jabkey us aurat key paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba aksar aatey jatey rehtey they. phir aap ney farmaya : to ibn-Ummey Maktoom key yahan iddat guzar. wo na-bina shakhs hai. phir jab teri iddat puri ho jaey to mujhey batlaanaa. jab meri iddat khatam ho gaee to mainey aap ko batlaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey shaadi ka pegham kis kis ney bheja hai? mainey kaha : eik to Muawiya ney aur eik Quraishi shakhs ney. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Muawiya to Quraish key nojawanon mein sey eik nojawan hai. uskey paas koi maal waghera nahin. aur doosra shakhs (Abu-Jahm) biwiyon ki bahut ziyada pitney wala hai, is mein bhalai nahin hai. lekin to Usama bin Zaid sey nikah kar ley. mujhey ye baat achchhi na lagi lekin aap ney teen dafa yehi kaha to mainey Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) sey nikah kar liya."
3247,"Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke (merey khawind) Abu-Amr bin Hafs (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujhey pakki Talaq dey di jabkey wo merey paas mojud na they. to unkey wakeel ney merey paas kuchh jau waghera bhejey. mainey wo pasand na kiye. wakeel kehney laga : Allah ki qism ! terey liye to hamarey zimmey kuchh banta hi nahin. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaee aur sari soorate-haal bata di. aap ney farmaya : terey liye kharcha (khawind key zimmey) nahin banta. isi ke sath aap ney mujhey Hazrat Umme-Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar iddat guzarney ka mashwara diya. phir aap (khud hi) farmaney lagey is aurat key paas merey (mehman) sahaba aatey jatey rehtey hain, lihaza to ibne Ummey Maktoom key yahan iddat guzar ley kyonkey wo na-bina shakhs hai. to wahan apney (faaltu) kapdey utaar sakti hai. phir jab teri iddat puri ho jaey to mujhey ittilaa karna. jab meri iddat puri ho gaee to mainey aap ko bataya ke Hazrat Muawiya bin Abi Sufiyan aur Abu-Jahm (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujhey shaadi ka pegham bheja hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Abu-Jahm to har waqt kandhey par lathi uthaey rakhta hai, kabhi nahin utaarta aur raha Muawiya ! to wo faqir hai. uskey paas ziyada maal nahin. lekin to Usama sey nikah kar ley. mainey napasand kiya. aap ney phir farmaya : to Usama sey nikah kar ley. chunanche mainey un sey nikah kar liya. to Allah Taala ney us nikah mein bhalai aur barkat dali yahan tak ke mujh par rashk kiya gaya."
3248,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke ansaar mein sey eik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur kehney laga : mainey ansaar ki eik aurat ko shaadi ka pegham bheja hai. aap ney farmaya : tu ney usey dekha nahin? ansaar ki aakhon mein kuchh kharabi hoti hai. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke mainey eik aur jagah ye hadees is tarah pai hai ke Yazid bin Kaisaan ney Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah sey bayan kiya, jabkey sahih ye hai ke riwayat Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey hai."
3249,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney eik ( Ansari ) aurat sey shaadi karney ka irada kiya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey dekh lena, kyonkey ansaar ki aakhon mein kuchh kharabi hoti hai."
3250,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke (meri beti) Hafsa binte umr (Raziallahu anhu) Khunais bin Huzaafa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bewa ho gaeen. ye Khunais Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba mein sey they. Badr mein bhi hazir huye they. Madina Munawra mein faut ho gaey. main Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila aur unhen Hafsa sey nikah ki pesh kaash! ki. mainey kaha : agar aap munasib samjhen to main Hafsa ka nikah aap sey kar dun? wo kehney lagey : main is barey mein ghor aur fikr karunga. chand din guzrey to main phir unhen mila to wo kehney lagey : aaj kal mera nikah karney ka irada nahin hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : phir main Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila aur un sey kaha : agar aap pasand farmaain to main Hafsa ka nikah aap sey kar dun? unhoney mujhey kuch jawab na diya. mujhey un par Hazrat Usman sey bhi badh kar narazi thi. chand din baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey unkey nikah ka pegham bhej diya. mainey (khushi aur khoobi ke sath) aap sey Hafsa ka nikah kar diya. baad mein mujhey Abu-Bakar miley aur kehney lagey : shayad aap us waqt mujh sey naraz ho gaey hongey jab aap ney mujhey Hafsa key nikah ki paish-kash ki thi aur mainey aap ko koi jawab nahin diya tha. mainey kaha : haan. wo kehney lagey ke jab aap ney mujhey paish-kash ki thi to aap ko jawab deney sey mujhey koi chiz maanea' (rukawat) nahin thi magar ye ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko un (Hafsa) ka tazkira farmatey suna tha. aur main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka raz faash nahin kar sakta tha. han, agar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unhein pegham na bhejtey to main un sey nikah kar leta."
3251,Hazrat Sabit Banaani sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key paas tha jabkey un ki eik beti bhi unkey paas mojud thi. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui aur us ney aap ko nikah ki paish-kash ki aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aap ko mujh sey nikah ki zarurat hai?
3252,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke eik aurat ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko nikah ki paish-kash ki. (ye sun kar) Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki eik beti hansney lagi aur kaha : wo aurat kis qadr kam-haya wali thi. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : wo tujh sey ziyada behtar thi ke us ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko nikah ki paish-kash ki.
3253,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab Hazrat Zainab (binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha)) ki iddat khatam hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (unkey saabiq (pichhle) khawind) Zaid (bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu)) sey farmaya : usey meri taraf sey nikah ka pegham do. Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey ja kar kaha : Zainab ! khush ho jaao, mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney terey paas nikah ka pegham dey kar bheja hai. wo kehney lagin : main koi faisla nahin karungi yahan tak ke apney Rab taala sey mashwara kar lun. wo apni namaz-gaah ki taraf uthin aur (namaz istikhaara shuru kar li). udhar Quran Majeed (ka hukm ) utar aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur un ki ijazat key baghair (unkey hujrey mein) dakhil ho gaey."
3254,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Zainab binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki dusri azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) par fakhr kiya karti thin ke Allah Taala ney mera nikah aasmano par farmaya, isi ke sath unkey barey mein pardey wali aayat utri."
3255,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamein tamam maamlat mein istikhaara (ki dua) sikhatey they jis tarah hamein Quran Majeed ki sura sikhatey they. aap farmatey they : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs kisi kaam ka irada karey to wo farz namaz key ilawa do rakat nafl ada kerey. phir yun kahe : (اَللّٰھُمَّ اِنِّیْ أَسْتَخِیْرُکَ بِعِلْمِکَ … ثُمَّ أَرْضِنِیی بِہ), ''aey Allah ! main terey ilm key zariey sey tujh sey khair ka Talib hun aur teri qudrat key zariey sey tujh sey madad ka talabgar hun. aur tujh sey terey azeem Fazal ka sawali hun (ya terey azeem Fazal ki wajeh sey tujh sey sawal karta hun) kyonkey to har chiz par qudrat rakhta hai, main qudrat nahin rakhta aur to sab kuchh janta hai, main nahin janta. to tamam ghaibon ko ba-khoobi jan'ney wala hai. aey Allah ! agar to janta hai ke ye kaam merey Deen aur duniya aur anjam kaar key lihaz sey … ya aap ney farmaya : duniya aur aakhirat key lihaz sey … behtar hai to to isey merey liye muqaddar kar dey aur isey merey liye aasan farma dey, phir merey liye is mein barkat farma. aur agar to janta hai ke ye kaam merey Deen aur duniya aur anjam kaar key lihaz sey, ya duniya aur aakhirat key lihaz sey, bura (nuqsan deh) hai to is kaam ko mujh sey door farma aur mera rukh bhi is sey pher dey aur jahan bhi khair ho merey liye muqaddar farma. aur phir mujhey is par razi kar dey. aap ney farmaya : wo (dua mein) apney kaam ka bhi zikr kerey."
3256,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke jab meri iddat khatam ho gaee to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney merey paas apney nikah ka pegham bheja. mainey qubul na kiya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko apney nikah ka pegham dey kar bheja. mainey kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey arz karen ke main bahut ghairat wali aurat hun (aap ki dusri biwiyon sey nibah na ho sakeyga). phir merey (sabiqa (pichhle) khawind sey merey) bachchey bhi hain, isi ke sath us waqt merey auliyaa mein sey koi yahan mojud nahin. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur aap sey ye baaten zikr kin. aap ney farmaya : dobara jaao aur usey kaho : tumhara ye kehna ke main ghairat wali aurat hun, 'to main Allah Taala sey dua karunga ke Allah Taala teri (be-ja) ghairat ko khatam kar dey. aur tumhara ye kehna ke merey bachchey hain, 'to tujhey un ki fikr nahin kerni chahiye, unhen kharcha waghera diya jaeyga. baqi rahi tumhari ye baat ke merey auliyaa mein sey koi hazir nahin, 'to sun ley ke terey auliyaa mein sey koi shakhs bhi chahey wo hazir ho ya ghaaieb, is kaam ko napasand nahin kerega. mainey apney betey sey kaha : aey umr ! utho aur mera Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey nikah kar do. chunanche us ney aap sey mera nikah kar diya. ye hadees mukhtasar bayan ki gaee hai."
3257,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey nikah farmaya to wo chhe saal ki thin aur unhen apney ghar basaya to nau saal ki thin.
3258,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey saatwen saal mein nikah kiya aur main nau saal ki hui to mujhey apney ghar basaya.
3259,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey nau saal ki umr mein apney ghar abad farmaya aur main nau saal aap ki mubarak sohbat mein rahi.
3260,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey shaadi farmaai to wo no saal ki thin. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut huye to wo atthaara saal ki thin.
3261,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab (meri beti) Hafsa binte umr apney khawind Hazrat Khunais bin Huzaafa Sahami (Raziallahu anhu) sey bewa ho gaee … aur ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahabi they aur Madina Munawra mein faut huye … to main Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaya aur unhen Hafsa sey nikah ki paish-kash ki. mainey kaha : agar aap chahen to main aap ka nikah Hafsa sey kar dun. wo kehney lagey : main ghor karunga. chand din guzar gaey to wo mujhey miley aur kehney lagey : mera khayal hai ke main in dino nikah na karun. Hazrat umr ney kaha : phir main Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila aur kaha : agar aap chahen to main aap ka nikah Hafsa sey kar dun. Abu-Bakar chup ho gaey. mujhey koi jawab na diya. mujhey Usman ki nisbat un par ziyada ghussa tha. chand din guzar gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey nikah ka pegham bhej diya aur mainey aap sey us ka nikah kar diya, phir mujhey Abu-Bakar miley aur kehney lagey : shayad us waqt aap mujh par naraz ho gaey they jab aap ney mujhey Hazrat Hafsa key nikah ki paish-kash ki thi aur mainey aap ko koi jawab nahin diya tha? mainey kaha : bilkul. wo kehney lagey : aap ney jo mujhey paish-kash ki thi us ka jawab deney mein mujhey koi chiz maanea' (rukawat) nahin thi magar mujhey ilm tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey nikah ka zikr farmaya tha. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka raz faash nahin kar sakta tha. albatta agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) nikah na farmatey to main zarur nikah kar leta."
3262,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bewa aurat apney nikah key barey mein apney wali sey ziyada ikhtiyar rakhti hai aur kanwari ladki sey bhi uskey nikah key barey mein ijazat li jaey. aur uski ijazat us ka khamosh rehna (inkar na karna) hai.
3263,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bewa aurat apney barey mein apney wali sey ziyada ikhtiyar rakhti hai aur nabaligh ya kanwari ladki sey bhi ijazat li jaey. aur us ka khamosh rehna uski taraf sey ijazat hoga.
3264,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bewa apney mamley mein ziyada ikhtiyar rakhti hai. aur kanwari ladki sey bhi uski zaat key mutalliq mashwara kiya jaeyga, albatta uski khamoshi uski ijazat (ki daleel) hai."
3265,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bewa key muqabley mein wali ko ikhtiyar nahin aur nabaligh ya kanwari sey bhi mashwara kar liya jaey. agar wo khamosh rahey to ye uski taraf sey iqrar aur ijazat hai.
3266,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bewa aurat apney (nikah key) barey mein ziyada ikhtiyar rakhti hai. aur kanwari ladki sey bhi us ka baap ijazat hasil kerey. aur uski khamoshi ijazat hi hai.
3267,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bewa ka nikah na kiya jaey yahan tak ke us sey ijazat hasil kar li jaey. aur kanwari ladki ka bhi nikah na kiya jaey yahan tak ke us sey mashwara kar liya jaey. sahaba ney puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! uski ijazat kaisey malum hogi? aap ney farmaya : uski ijazat ye hai ke wo khamosh rahey.
3268,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurton sey unkey nikah key barey mein mashwara kiya karo. kaha gaya ke kanwari ladki to sharmaaeygi aur chup raheygi. aap ney farmaya : yehi uski ijazat hai.
3269,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bewa aurat ka nikah na kiya jaey yahan tak ke us sey mashwara liya jaey aur kanwari ladki ka bhi nikah na kiya jaey yahan tak ke us sey ijazat li jaey. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! uski ijazat kaisey malum hogi? aap ney farmaya : ye ke wo khamosh rahey.
3270,"Hazrat Khansaa binte Khizaam (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unkey walid ney us ka nikah kar diya jabkey wo bewa thi. chunanche us (Khansaa) ney is (nikah) ko napasand kiya, bil-aakhir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui (aur aap sey puri baat bata di) to aap ney us (key walid) ka kiya huwa nikah khatam kar diya."
3271,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik nojawan ladki unkey paas aai aur kaha : merey walid ney mera nikah apney bhateejey sey kar diya hai taake meri wajeh sey us ka martaba ooncha kerey. jabkey main usey pasand nahin karti. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key tashrif laney tak beth ja. itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi tashrif ley aaye to us ney puri baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko batai. aap ney uskey walid ko bulaya aur nikah ka ikhtiyar us ladki key supurd kar diya. wo ladki kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney walid mohtaram key kiye huye nikah ko barqarar rakhti hun. main to ye jan'na chahti thi ke aurton ko bhi is (nikah key) mamley mein kuchh ikhtiyar hai ya nahin?
3272,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : yatim bachchi sey uskey nikah key barey mein mashwara kiya jaey. agar wo chup rahey to yehi uski ijazat hai. agar wo inkar kar dey to is par zabardasti nahin ki ja sakti.
3273,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Memuna binte Haris (Raziallahu anhu) sey ehraam ki haalat mein, Hazrat Yaala ki riwayat ke mutabiq 'maqame-sar'  mein nikah farmaya."
3274,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey ehraam ki haalat mein nikah farmaya.
3275,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey ehraam ki haalat mein nikah farmaya. Hazrat Memuna ney apna wakeel Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko muqarrar farmaya tha, lihaza unhoney aap sey unka nikah kar diya."
3276,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey ehraam ki haalat mein nikah farmaya.
3277,Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Mohrim (ehraam ki halat mein) na apna nikah karey na kisi ka kiraey aur na nikah ka pegham bhejey.
3278,Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Mohrim (ehraam ki halat mein) apna nikah karey na kisi ka kiraey aur na nikah ka pegham bhejey.
3279,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein namaz mein tashahud aur dusri haajaat (zaruraton) (khutba nikah waghera) main tashahud sikhlaya. hajate-nikah waghera wala tashahud ye hai :( أَنِ الْحَمدُ لِلّٰہِ … أَنَّ مُحَمَّداً عَبْدُہُ وَرَسُوْلُہُ ),''sab tareef Allah hi key liye hai. hum us sey madad talab kartey hain aur hum us sey bakhshish talab kartey hain aur apney nafson ki shararaton sey (bachney key liye) uski panah mein aatey hain. jis shakhs ko Allah Taala hidayat dey, usey koi gumrah karney wala nahin aur jisey Allah Taala gumrah kar dey, usey koi hidayat deney wala nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. phir aap teen aayaat padhtey.''"
3280,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kisi masley mein baat cheet ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney yun khutba irshad farmaya : (أِنَّ الْحَمدَ لِلّٰہِ نَحْمَدُہُ وَنَسْتَعِیْنُہُ … أَمَّا بَعْدُ),''tareef Allah hi key liye hai. hum uski tareef kartey hain aur hum us sey madad talab kartey hain. jisey Allah Taala hidayat dey, usey koi gumrah karney wala nahin. aur jisey wo gumrah kar dey, usey koi hidayat deney wala nahin. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. wo akela hai. us ka koi shareek nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. hamd aur durud key baad … ."
3281,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke do aadmiyon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein khutba diya. un mein sey eik ney kaha : jo Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat kerega, wo hidayat yafta hoga, aur jo in dono ki nafarmani kerega, wo gumrah hoga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to bura khateeb hai."
3282,"Hazrat Sahal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key yahan kuchh logon mein betha tha ke eik aurat aa kar kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney aap ko aap key nikah key liye pesh karti hun. aap merey barey mein jo munasib samjhen faisla farmaeyn. aap chup ho gaey aur usey kuchh jawab na diya. wo dobara khadi ho kar kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney aap ko aap key sath nikah key liye pesh karti hun. aap merey barey mein jo chahen faisla farmaeyn. (aap phir chup rahey to) eik aadmi khada huwa aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! (agar aap ko zarurat nahin to) is aurat ka nikah mujh sey farma dijiye. aap ney farmaya : terey paas (mehar waghera key liye) koi chiz hai? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : jaao, talash karo chahey lohey ki anguthi hi ho. wo gaya, talash key baad wapis aaya aur kehney laga : mujhey koi chiz nahin mili, lohey ki anguthi bhi nahin. aap ney farmaya : tujhey kuchh Quran yad hai. us ney kaha : ji haan ! mujhey falan falan suraten hifz hain. aap ney farmaya : mainey Quran Majeed ki in Suraton (ki taaleem) key iwaz tera us sey nikah kar diya."
3283,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shart puri karna sab sey ziyada zaroori hai, wo hai jis key sath tum aurton ko apney liye halal kartey ho."
3284,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shart ko pura karna sab sey ziyada zaroori hai, wo hai jis key sath tum aurton ko apney liye halal kartey ho."
3285,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Hazrat Rifaa (Raziallahu anhu) ki (pichhli) biwi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa kar kaha : Rifaa ney mujhey Talaq di aur Talaq bitta (teesri Talaq) di. mainey uskey baad Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber sey nikah kar liya magar uskey paas to kapdey key pallu (kinarey, yani mardaana kamzori) ka sa maamla hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (us ki is tamseel (example) par) muskuraaey aur farmaya : shayad to dobara Rifaa key paas jana chahti hai? to nahin ja sakti yahan tak ke wo tujh sey lutf andoz ho aur to us sey lutf andoz ho."
3286,"Hazrat Zainab binte Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) jin ki walida Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki Zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) thin, ney bataya ke mujhey Hazrat Umme-Habiba binte Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anha) ney batlaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya ke aap meri behan binte Abi Sufiyan sey nikah kar lein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya to usey pasand karti hai? mainey kaha : ji haan. main kon sa aap key ghar mein akeli hun? aur meri behan merey sath is khair (aap ki zojiyat (nikah)) main shareek ho jaey to mujhey is sey badh kar kon si chiz pasandida hogi? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teri behan merey liye halal nahin. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! hum to aapas mein ye tabsire karti rehti hain ke aap Darra binte Abi Salma sey nikah karna chahtey hain. aap ney farmaya : Umme-Salma ki beti sey? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! agar wo meri biwi ki pichhlag beti (merey ghar mein) na bhi  (reh rahi) hoti, phir bhi merey liye halal na hoti kyonkey wo merey razaai (doodh-shareek) bhai ki beti hai. mujhey aur Abu-Salma ko Soobiya ney doodh pilaya tha, lihaza tum mujh sey nikah key liye apni betiyan aur behney pesh na kiya karo."
3287,"Hazrat Zainab binte Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri behan sey nikah kar lein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to ye baat pasand karti hai? unhoney kaha : ji haan. main kon sa aap key ghar mein akeli hun? aur meri behan is fazilat mein merey sath shareek ho jaey, is sey ziyada pasandida baat kya ho sakti hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye halal nahin. Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum to ye tabsirey karti rehti hain ke aap Darra binte Abu-Salma sey nikah karney waley hain. aap ney farmaya : Umme-Salma ki beti? unhoney kaha : ji haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! agar wo meri biwi ki pichhlag beti na hoti tab bhi wo merey liye halal na thi kyonkey wo merey razaai (doodh-shareek) bhai ki beti hai. mujhey aur Abu-Salma ko Soobiya ney doodh pilaya tha, lihaza tum mujh par nikah key liye apni betiyan aur behney pesh na kiya karo."
3288,"Hazrat Zainab bint Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan kiya ke Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : tehqiq hum ye baaten karti rehti hain ke aap an-qareeb Darra binte Abi Salma sey nikah farmaney waley hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya Umme-Salma sey nikah key baad? isi ke sath agar mainey Umme-Salma sey nikah na bhi kya hota, tab bhi wo merey liye halal nahin thi kyonkey us (Darra) ka baap (Hazrat Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu)) mera razaai (doodh-shareek) bhai tha."
3289,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aap ko meri behan sey kuchh raghbat (dilchaspi) hai? aap ney farmaya : main kya karun? mainey kaha : is sey nikah kar lein. aap ney farmaya : kya tujhey ye pasand hai? mainey kaha : ji han, main pehley bhi to aap key ghar mein akeli nahin. aur meri behan is fazilat mein merey sath shareek ho jaey to mujhey ye bahut pasand hai. aap ney farmaya : wo to merey liye halal nahin hai. mainey kaha : mujhey to ye baat pahunchi hai ke aap Darra binte Umme-Salma sey nikah ka irada rakhtey hain. aap ney farmaya : Abu-Salma ki beti sey? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! agar wo meri biwi ki beti na hoti tab bhi merey liye halal na thi kyonkey wo merey razaai (doodh-shareek) bhai ki beti hai. tum mujh par apni betiyan aur behney nikah key liye pesh na kiya karo."
3290,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi aurat aur uski phuphi ya kisi aurat aur uski khaala sey (ba-yak waqt) nikah na kiya jaey.
3291,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke eik aurat aur uski phuphi ya eik aurat aur uski khaala sey eik hi waqt mein nikah kiya jaey.
3292,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke kisi aurat sey uski phuphi ya khaala key nikah par nikah kiya jaey.
3293,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney chaar aurton sey eik hi waqt mein nikah karney sey mana farmaya : aurat aur uski phuphi. isi tarah koi aurat aur uski khaala.
3294,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi aurat sey uski phuphi ya uski khaala key nikah par nikah na kiya jaey.
3295,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke kisi aurat sey uski phuphi ya uski khaala key nikah par nikah kiya jaey.
3296,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi aurat sey uski phuphi ya khaala key sath nikah hotey huye nikah na kiya jaey.
3297,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi aurat sey uski phuphi ya khaala key nikah par nikah na kiya jaey.
3298,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke kisi aurat sey uski phuphi key nikah par nikah kiya jaey ya phuphi sey uski bhatiji key nikah par nikah kiya jaey.
3299,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi aurat sey uski phuphi ya uski khaala key sath nikah ki mojudgi mein nikah na kiya jaey."
3300,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke kisi aurat sey uski phuphi ya khaala key nikah par nikah kiya jaey.
3301,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi aurat sey uski phuphi ya khaala key nikah par nikah karney sey mana farmaya.
3302,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo rishtey paidaaishi nasab ki wajeh sey haram hain, razaat (doodh pilaaney) ki wajeh sey bhi haram hain."
3303,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke unka razaai (doodh shareek) chacha jis ka naam Aflah tha, ney unkey yahan aaney ki ijazat talab ki to unhoney us sey parda kiya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko batlaya gaya to aap ney farmaya : Aaisha ! us sey parda na karo kyonkey razaat (doodh pilaney) ki bina par wo sab rishtey haram ho jatey hain jo nasab ki bina par haram hotey hain."
3304,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : razaat (doodh pilaney) ki bina par wo sab rishtey (nikah key liye) haram ho jatey hain jo nasab ki wajeh sey haram ho jatey hain.
3305,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : razaat (doodh pilaney) ki wajeh sey wo sab rishtey (nikah key liye) haram ho jatey hain jo paidaaishi nasab ki wajeh sey haram hotey hain.
3306,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya wajeh hai ke aap Quraish (key deegar qabaayel) main to faraakh dili sey rishtey farma rahey hain magar hamen (banu haashim ko) mehroom rakh rahey hain? aap ney farmaya : terey paas koi (rishta) hai? mainey kaha : ji haan ! Hamza ki beti hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo to merey liye halal nahin kyonkey wo merey razaai (doodh shareek) bhai ki beti hai.
3307,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey Hazrat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti (sey nikah kerney) ka zikr kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : bilashuba wo merey razaai (doodh shareek) bhai ki beti hai.
3308,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey Hazrat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti key sath nikah karney ka mutalba kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : bilashuba wo merey razaai (doodh shareek) bhai ki beti hai aur yaqinan razaat (doodh pilaney) ki bina par wo sab rishtey haram ho jatey hain jo nasab ki bina par haram hotey hain.
3309,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah Taala ney Quran Majeed mein jo ehkam nazil farmaey, un mein sey eik ye tha ke bachcha das dafa kisi aurat ka wazeh taur par doodh pi ley to un sey hurmat sabit ho jati hai. phir ye hukm mansookh (khatm) kar key hurmat ka hukm paanch dafa wazeh taur par doodh peeney par laagu kar diya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut huye to ye hukm Quran mein padha jata tha."
3310,Hazrat Ummey Fazl (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey razaat (doodh pilaney) key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : eik do ghoont ya eik do dafa choosnaa hurmat ko sabit nahin karta.
3311,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik do dafa choosnaa hurmat ko sabit nahin karta.
3312,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik do ghoont ya eik do dafa choosnaa hurmat sabit nahin kartey.
3313,Hazrat Qatada sey riwayat hai ke hamney Hazrat Ibrahim bin Yazid Nakhai ki taraf razaat (doodh pilaney) key barey mein sawal likh bheja. unhoney jawab mein likha ke Hazrat Shureh ney hum sey bayan farmaya ke Hazrat Ali aur Hazrat ibne-Masood Raziallahu anhuma thodi ya ziyada razaat (doodh pilaney) sey hurmat key qaail they. unkey tahreeri jawab mein ye bhi likha tha ke hamein Hazrat Abul-Sha'a-Sa'a Mahaaribi ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya kartey they : jald bazi main eik do dafa choosnaa hurmat ka sabab nahin banta.
3314,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey yahaan tashrif laye to merey paas eik aadmi betha huwa tha. ye baat aap par bahut shaaq guzri aur mainey aap key chehre-anwar par narazi key asraat mehsus kiye. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye mera razaai (doodh shareek) bhai hai. aap ney farmaya : achi tarah dekh liya karo ke tumharey razaai (doodh shareek) bhai kon hain? kyonkey razaat (doodh pilana) us daur mein moatabar hai jab doodh hi bhook mitata ho.
3315,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey yahaan tashrif farma they. mainey suna ke eik aadmi Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) key ghar mein dakhil honey ki ijazat mang raha hai. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye aadmi aap (ki biwi) key ghar mein dakhil honey ki ijazat talab kar raha hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera khayal hai, ye falan shakhs hai, Hafsa ka razaai (doodh shareek) chacha. mainey eik razaai (doodh shareek) chacha ka naam letey huye kaha : agar falan shakhs zinda hota to wo merey ghar aa sakta tha? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : doodh peena bhi un sab rishton ko haram kar deta hai jinhen nasbi rishta haram karta hai."
3316,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mera razaai (doodh shareek) chacha Abul-Ja'd mujhey milney aaya magar mainey usey ghar mein dakhil na honey diya. aur Hisham ney kaha : wo Abul Qaies tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghar mein tashrif laye to mainey aap ko sara waqia batlaya. aap ney farmaya : usey ghar mein aaney ki ijazat do.
3317,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke (unkey razaai (doodh shareek) baap) Abul Qaies ka bhai pardey wali aayat utarney key baad Aaisha key paas aaya aur andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki to usney ijazat deney sey inkar kar diya. ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney zikr ki gaee to aap ney (un sey) farmaya : usey ijazat do. bilashuba wo tumhara chacha hai. mainey arz kiya : mujhey to aurat hi ney doodh pilaya tha na ke mard ney. aap ney farmaya : nahin. bilashuba wo tera chacha hai. terey paas aa sakta hai.
3318,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke (merey razaai (doodh shareek) walid) Abul Qaies key bhai Aflah ney merey paas aaney ki ijazat talab ki. jabkey wo mera razaai (doodh shareek) chacha tha. mainey usey ijazat deney sey inkar kar diya, yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to mainey aap ko puri baat batai. aap ney farmaya : usey ijazat dey diya karo bilashuba wo tumhara chacha hai. ye waqia pardey ka hukm utarney key baad ka hai."
3319,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke merey (razaai (doodh shareek)) chacha Aflah ney pardey key ehkam utarney key baad merey paas aaney ki ijazat talab ki. mainey unhen ijazat na di. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to mainey aap sey puchha. aap ney farmaya : unhen ijazat dey diya karo. wo tumharey chacha hain. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey aurat ney doodh pilaya hai na ke mard ney. aap ney farmaya : unhen ijazat do. terey haath khaak aalud hon. wo tumharey chacha hi hain.
3320,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke merey razaai (doodh shareek) baap Abul Qaies key bhai Aflah aaye aur andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki. mainey kaha : main unhen ijazat nahin dungi yahan tak ke main Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochh lun. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to mainey aap sey kaha : Abul Qaies key bhai Aflah aaye they. andar aaney ki ijazat talab kartey they. mainey unhen ijazat deney sey inkar kar diya. aap ney farmaya : unhen ijazat dey diya karo kyonkey wo tumharey chacha hain. mainey kaha : mujhey Aul Qaies ki biwi ney doodh pilaya hai na ke Abul Qaies ney. aap ney farmaya : unhein ijazat dey diya karo, wo tumharey chacha hi hain."
3321,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Sahla binte Suhail, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui aur kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! Saalim key merey paas aaney janey ki wajeh sey main (apney khawind) Abu-Huzaifa key chehrey par karaahat key aasaar dekhti hun (kya karun?). aap ney farmaya : to usey doodh pila dey. mainey kaha : wo to dadhi wala hai. aap ney farmaya : doodh pila dey, is sey Abu-Huzaifa key chehrey ki karaahat khatam ho jaeygi. wo farmati hain : uskey baad mainey kabhi Hazrat Abu-Huzaifa key chehrey par karaahat mehsus nahin ki."
3322,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Sahla binte Suhail (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ayin aur kehney lagin : main Salim key apney paas aaney janey ki wajeh sey apney khawind Abu-Huzaifa key chehrey par karaahat key aasaar mehsus karti hun. aap ney farmaya : usey doodh pila dey. wo kehney lagi : usey kaisey doodh pilaaun? wo to pura aadmi hai? aap ney farmaya : kya main nahin janta ke wo pura aadmi hai? phir wo baad mein aai aur kehney lagi : qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko bar-haq Nabi banaya ! mainey iskey baad Abu-Huzaifa key chehrey mein zarra bhar bhi karaahat mehsus nahin ki.
3323,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ko hukm diya tha ke wo Saalim Mola Abu-Huzaifa ko doodh pila dey taake Abu-Huzaifa ki ghairat (us key aaney janey par) na bhadke. unhoney usey doodh pila diya, halanke wo pura mard tha. Rabeea raawi ney kaha : ye (rukhsat (chhoot)) Hazrat Salim key liye thi."
3324,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Sahla (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai aur kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! Saalim hamarey yahaan (bila rok tok) aata jata rehta hai lekin ab wo mardon ki tarah (jinsi maamlat) samajhney laga hai aur un baaton ko janney laga hai jinhen mard samajhtey hain. aap ney farmaya : to usey doodh pila dey. phir us wajeh sey to uskey liye haram ho jaeygi. (raawi hadees ibne Abi Muleka ney kaha : ) main eik baras thehra raha, ye hadees bayan nahin karta tha. main Qasim sey mila to usney kaha : ye hadees bayan kiya kar aur kisi sey bhi na dar."
3325,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Saalim Mola Abi Huzefa (munh bole betey honey ki wajeh sey) Hazrat Abu-Huzaifa aur un ki biwi key sath unkey ghar hi mein rehta tha, phir (Abu-Huzaifa ki biwi Sahla) binte Suhail (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai aur kehney lagi : Salim ab pura mard ban gaya hai aur wo mardon wali (makhsus) baaten samajhney laga hai. wo hamarey paas (ab bhi usi tarah) aata jata hai. main uski wajeh sey Hazrat Abu-Huzaifa key dil mein kuchh karaahat mehsus karti hun to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to usey doodh pila dey. to is par haram ho jaeygi. (woh kehti hain : ) mainey usey doodh pila diya. is tarah Hazrat Abu-Huzaifa key dil ki karaahat khatam ho gaee. main dobara aap key paas aai aur kehney lagi : mainey usey doodh pila diya tha. is tarah Abu-Huzaifa key dil ki Nagawari khatam ho gaee."
3326,"Hazrat Urwa sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key ilawa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki tamam pak biviyan is baat sey munkir thin ke logon mein sey koi shakhs is qism yani badi umr ki razaat key rishtey sey unkey paas aaye-jaey. unhoney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey bhi kaha tha ke Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney jo hukm Sahla bint Suhail ko diya tha, wo sirf Salim key sath khas tha. aur wo unkey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf sey khususi rukhsat thi. Allah ki qasam! is qism ki razaat key rishtey sey koi shakhs na hamarey ghar aa sakta hai aur na hamen be hijaab dekh sakta hai."
3327,"Hazrat Umme-Salma Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma farmaya karti thin ke baqi tamam azwaj (jodey) Nabi Raziallahu anhunna is baat ki qaail na thin ke koi shakhs is qism ki razaat key sath unkey paas aaye-jaey balke unhoney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey bhi kaha tha : Allah ki qasam! hum to isey aisi rukhsat samajhti hain jo Allah Taala key Rasool ney khususi taur par Hazrat Salim ko ata farmaai thi, lihaza koi shakhs us jaisi razaat key rishtey sey hamarey yahan na aaye-jaey aur na hamen dekhey."
3328,Hazrat Judama bint Wahab (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera irada tha ke main logon ko muddate-razaat mein jima karney sey rok dun lekin mujhey pata chala ke Farsi aur Rumi ye kaam kartey hain aur us sey unkey (doodh peetey) bachon ko koi nuqsan nahin hota.
3329,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas azl ka zikr kya gaya to aap ney farmaya : wo kya hota hai? hamney kaha : kisi aadmi key nikah mein koi aurat ho, wo us sey jima karta ho lekin hamal ko napasand karta ho ya uski laundi ho, wo us sey jima karta ho lekin uskey hamila honey ko napasand karta ho. aap ney farmaya : aisey na karo to bhi kuch na hoga. asal baat to taqdir ki hai."
3330,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Zarqi sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey azl key barey mein puchha. usney kaha : meri biwi bachey ko doodh pila rahi hai. main pasand nahin karta ke usey hamal thehrey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : reham key barey mein jo muqaddar hai, wo to ho kar rahega (ya jis chiz ka reham mein pahunchna muqaddar hai wo to pahunch kar rahegi."
3331,Hazrat Hujjaaj (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon si chiz razaat ka haq ada kar sakti hai? aap ney farmaya : eik ghulam ya laundi (razai walida ko dey do ).
3332,"Hazrat Aqba bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey eik aurat sey shaadi ki to hamarey paas eik kalay rang ki aurat aai aur kehney lagi : mainey to tum dono ko doodh pilaya hai. (is liye tumhara nikah durust nahin. ) main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur aap sey pura waqia bayan kya aur mainey kaha : mainey eik aurat fulan binte-falan sey shaadi ki hai. merey paas eik kalay rang ki aurat aai aur kehney lagi : mainey tum dono ko doodh pilaya hai. aap ney mujh sey munh mod liya. main phir aap key chehra anwar ki janib aaya aur kaha ke wo jhoot bolti hai. aap ney farmaya : to kaisey us (apni biwi) key sath reh sakta hai jab ke wo kehti hai ke usney tum dono ko doodh pilaya hai, usey chhod dey."
3333,"Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke main apney mamu ko mila jab ke unkey paas eik jhanda tha. mainey kaha : kahan ka irada hai? unhoney farmaya : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ki taraf bheja hai jisney apney walid ki wafat key baad uski mankuha biwi sey nikah kar liya tha, ke main uski gardan utaar dun, ya usey qatl kar dun."
3334,Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main apney chacha jaan ko mila to unkey paas jhanda tha. mainey kaha : kahan ka irada hai? wo kehney lagey : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ki taraf bheja hai jisney apney baap ki biwi sey nikah kar liya hai. aap ney mujhey hukm diya hai ke main uski gardan utaar dun aur us ka maal chin lun.
3335,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maqam Autaas ki taraf eik lashkar bheja . unka dushman sey muqabla huwa. ladaai hui aur wo ghalib aa gaey. aur bahut si aisi qaidi aurten unkey haath lagen jinkey khawind mushrikon mein reh gaey they. musalmanon ney un sey jima karney mein gunah mehsus kya. Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaari : « { وَالْمُحْصِنٰتُ مِنَ النِّسَاءِ اِلاَّ ماَ … } » aur shaadi shuda aurton sey bhi nikah haram hai magar wo kafir aurten jo ( jang mein) tumharey haath lagen . yani un sey jima o nikah halal hai b-sharte-ke un ki iddat guzar jaey.
3336,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney shighaar sey mana farmaya hai.
3337,"Hazrat Imran bin Husein (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Islam mein « جَلَب , جَنَب » aur « شِغار » jayez nahin. aur jo shakhs loot-maar kerey. wo hum mein sey nahin."
3338,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Islam mein jalb, janb aur shighaar nahin. abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke ye shadeed ghalati hai. sahih riwayat Bishr ki hai."
3339,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney nikah shighaar sey mana farmaya hai. aur nikah shighaar ye hai ke eik shakhs dusrey shakhs sey apni beti ka nikah kar dey us shart par ke wo bhi apni beti ka nikah us sey kar dega aur un dono nikaahon mein koi mehar na ho.
3340,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney shighaar sey mana farmaya : raawi Ubedullah ney kaha : shighaar ye hai ke eik aadmi apni beti ka nikah dey is shart par ke doosra usey apni behan ka nikah dega.
3341,"Hazrat Sahal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa kar kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! main aap sey nikah ki paish-kash ley kar aai hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski taraf dekha. nazar ko ooncha neecha kiya aur phir sar jhuka liya. jab aurat ney dekha ke aap ney uski baabat koi faisla nahin sunaya to wo beth gaee. aap key sahaba mein sey eik aadmi uth khada huwa aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar aap ko is (khatoon) ki zarurat nahin to iska nikah mujh sey farma dijiye. aap ney farmaya : terey paas (mehar deney key liye) koi chiz hai? us ney kaha : nahin. Allah ki qism ! merey paas koi chiz nahin. aap ney farmaya : ja talash kar, agar-che lohey ki anguthi hi ho. wo gaya, phir wapis aaya aur kehney laga. Allah ki qism ! aey Allah key Rasool ! lohey ki anguthi bhi nahin hai. albatta merey paas ye tehband hai. is ka nisf (aadha) isey bator mehar deta hun. Hazrat Sahal ney farmaya : uskey paas ooper wali chadar bhi na thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye terey tehband ka kya keregi? agar to isey pehneyga to is aurat par is (tehband) sey kuchh bhi na hoga aur agar wo pehneygi to tujh par kuchh na hoga. tab wo aadmi beth gaya, yahan tak ke kafi der tak betha raha. phir wo uth kar chal diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey jata huwa dekh liya to aap ney uski baabat hukm diya aur usey wapis bulaya gaya. jab wo aaya to aap ney farmaya : tujhey kitna Quran yad hai? us ney kaha : mujhey falan falan sura yad hai. us ney kaee suraten shumar kin. aap ney farmaya : kya to in Suraton ko zabani (baghair dekhey) padh sakta hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : tujhey jo Quran yad hai, mainey uskey iwaz is aurat ko terey qabzey (nikah) main dey diya."
3342,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney (meri walida) Hazrat Ummey Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) sey nikah kiya to un dono key darmiyan (Abu Talha ka) Islam lana hi haq mehar qarar paya. (darasal) Ummey Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) Hazrat Abu-Talha sey pehley musalman ho gaee thin. Hazrat Abu-Talha ney unhen nikah ka pegham bheja to wo kehney lagin : main to musalman ho chuki hun agar tum bhi musalman ho jaao to main tum sey nikah kar lungi. tab wo musalman ho gaey. chunanche wohi (unka musalman hona hi) un dono key darmiyan haq mehar muqarrar huwa.
3343,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Ummey Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) ko nikah ka pegham bheja to unhoney kaha : aey Abu-Talha ! Allah ki qism ! terey jaisey shakhs ka pegham radd nahin kiya ja sakta lekin to kafir hai aur main Islam la chuki hun. merey liye tujh sey nikah karna jayez nahin. agar to musalman ho jaey to yehi mera mehar hoga aur main tujh sey uskey ilawa koi mehar na maangungi. wo musalman ho gaey aur unka Islam hi Hazrat Ummey Sulaim ka mehar qarar paya. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key shagrid Hazrat Sabit ney kaha : mainey kisi aur aurat key barey mein nahin suna ke us ka mehar Hazrat Ummey Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) key mehar Islam sey behtar ho. Hazrat Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney unkey sath zindagi guzari aur un sey unkey bachchey bhi huye.
3344,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ko azad farmaya aur un ki azadi hi ko unka mehar qarar diya.
3345,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ko azad (farma kar un sey nikah) farmaya aur un ki azadi ko unka mehar qarar diya. ye lafz Muhammad (bin Raafey) key hain.
3346,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen ashkhaas ko dugna ajr ata farmaya jaeyga : eik wo aadmi jis key paas apni laundi ho, wo usey ilm aur adab sikhaey aur behtareen ilm aur adab sikhaey. phir usey azad kar key us sey nikah kar ley. doosra wo ghulam jo Allah Taala ka haq (ibaadat) bhi ada karey aur apney malikon key huquq bhi purey kerey. teesra wo jo ehle-kitab mein sey musalman ho jaey."
3347,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apni laundi ko azad kar key us sey nikah kerey. usey dohra sawab milega.
3348,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey Allah key is farman key barey mein puchha : (وَاِنْ خِفْتُمْ اَلاَّ تُقْسِطُوْا … ),''aur agar tumhen khatra ho ke tum yatimon ki baabat insaf nahin kar sakogey to tum (dusri) aurton sey nikah karo jo tumhen pasand hon.'' unhoney farmaya : aey merey bhaanjey ! is (aayat mein yatimon) sey wo yatim bachi murad hai jo apney kisi sarparast key yahan parwarish pa rahi ho. aur uskey sath uskey maal mein shareek ho. sarparast ko uskey maal aur jamaal sey dilchaspi ho, is liye us sarparast ka irada ho ke us (yatim bachchi) sey nikah karey (taake uskey maal par qabza kerey) magar mehar muqarrar karney mein insaf sey kaam na ley, yani usey itna mehar na dey jo koi doosra usey dey sakta hai. to aisey sarpraston ko rok diya gaya ke un sey nikah karen siwaey iske ke wo unkey sath insaf karen aur unhen unkey martabey key mutabiq ziyada mehar den warna wo unkey ilawa dusri aurton sey nikah karen jo unhen pasand hon. Hazrat Urwa ney kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : phir iskey baad logon ney un yatim bachchiyon ki baabat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey istifsaar (sawal) kiya to Allah ney ye aayat utaari : (وَیَسْتَفْتُوْنَکَ فِی النِّسَاءِ … وَتَرْغَبُوْنَ اَنْ تَنْکِحُوْھُنَّ),""ye aap sey aurton key barey mein sawal kartey hain, keh dijiye ki Allah Taala tumhen unkey barey mein fatwaa deta hai aur jo kuchh tum par kitab mein padha jata hai, wo un yatim aurton key barey mein hai jinhen tum wo nahin detey jo unkey liye farz kiya gaya hai aur chahtey ho ke un sey nikah kar lo.''Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : jo Allah Taala ney ye farmaya hai ke tum par unkey ehkam Kitabu-llah mein padhey jatey hain. is sey murad wohi pehli aayat hai : (وَاِنْ خِفْتُمْ اَنْ لاَّ تُقْسِطُوْا فِی الْیَتَامیٰ … الخ),Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : dusri aayat mein Allah Taala ka ye farman : (وَتَرْغَبُوْنَ اَنْ تَنْکِحُوْھُنَّ),us sey murad wo yatim bachi hai jo apney sarparast key yahan parwarish pa rahi ho jab ke wo maal aur jamaal key lihaz sey kam ho. (unkey tarze-amal ki wajeh sey) unhen is yatim bachchi key sath nikah karney sey bhi rok diya gaya jis key maal aur jamaal mein un ki dilchaspi thi, magar insaf key sath kyonkey wo (maal aur jamaal kam honey ki surat mein) un sey koi dilchaspi na rakhtey they."
3349,Hazrat Abu-Salma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey mehar key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney saadhey baara oqiye par nikah kiye aur ye paanch sau dirham bantey hain.
3350,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hum mein tashrif farma they, mehar das oqiye hota tha."
3351,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : khabrdar ! aurton key mehar key masley mein had sey na badho. agar kasir (ziyaada) mehar duniya mein izzat ya Allah Taala key nazdik taqwey ka sabab hota to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey ziyada laaiq they, jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni azwaje-mutahrat (biwiyon) mein sey kisi ko baara oqiye sey ziyada mehar nahin diya, aur na aap ki kisi beti ko is sey ziyada mehar diya gaya. kabhi-kabhi koi shakhs mehar ziyada muqarrar kar leta hai yahan tak ke uskey dil mein apni biwi sey dushmani ho jati hai. yahan tak ke wo kehta hai ke mainey tumharey liye mishkeezey ki rassi ki takleef bardasht ki (badi musibat uthai) eik raawi hadees (Abu Ajfaa) ney kaha : main Arbon mein sirf paida huwa hun, khalis Arbi nahin is liye mujhey in alfaz (علق القربۃ) ka mafhoom malum nahin tha. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aur eik (namunasib) baat tum ye kehtey ho ke jo shakhs tumhari un jangon mein maara jata hai ya mar jata hai, tum kehtey ho, falan aadmi shaheed huwa ya shahadat ki maut mara. ho sakta hai us shakhs ney apney janwer ki pusht ya uskey paalaan aur kaathi ko soney ya chaandi sey laadaa ho aur uski niyat tijarat ki ho, is liye tum aisey na kaho balke tum is tarah kaho jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein maara jaey ya faut ho jaey, wo jannat mein jaeyga."
3352,Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey nikah kiya jabkey wo Habsha mein thin. unka nikah Najaashi ney kiya tha aur unhoney apney paas sey chaar hazar dirham mehar diya tha aur unhen rukhsati ka saman (zarurat) bhi apney paas sey diya aur unhen Hazrat Sharjeel bin Hasna (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Madina Munawra bhej diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein (Habsha mein) koi chiz nahin bheji thi. aap ki dusri aurton ka mehar chaar so dirham tha.
3353,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye to un par  sufraa key nishaanaat they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey sabab puchha to unhoney bataya ke mainey eik Ansari aurat sey shaadi kar li hai. aap ney farmaya : tu ney usey kya mehar diya? unhoney kaha : soney ka eik nawaah. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : waleema kar agar-che eik bakri hi ka ho.
3354,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey dekha to mujh par shaadi ki khushi key aasaar they. (aap ney puchha tu) mainey kaha : mainey eik Ansari aurat sey shaadi kar li hai. aap ney farmaya : mehar kitna diya? mainey kaha : soney ka nawaah.
3355,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke be-shak Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat key sath jis mehar par nikah kiya jaey ya jo Atiya ya wada nikah sey pehley diya jaey, wo sab kuchh aurat ka hai. albatta nikah key baad milney wala tohfa usi ka hoga jisey diya jaeyga. aur wo (behtareen) chiz jiski wajeh sey kisi ki izzat ki jaey, uski beti ya behan hai (jo wo kisi key nikah mein dey). ye alfaz Abdullah key hain."
3356,"Hazrat Alqama aur Aswad sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey eik aisey aadmi key barey mein sawal kiya gaya jisney kisi aurat sey nikah kiya magar mehar muqarrar na kiya, isi ke sath wo biwi key sath sohbat karney sey pehley hi faut ho gaya. Hazrat Abdullah ney farmaya : logon sey poochho kya us barey mein koi farmane-Rasool mojud hai? logon ney kaha : aey Abu Abdur-Rehman ! hum is barey mein koi farman nahin paatey. unhoney farmaya : (ab) main apni raey sey baat karta hun. agar meri baat durust hai to Allah ki taraf sey hogi. (meri raey ye hai ke) us aurat ko us jaisi dusri aurton key mutabiq mehar milega (yani mehar ke jaisi) na kam na ziyada. usey virasat bhi mileygi aur usey iddate-wafat bhi guzaarni hogi. itney mein Ashja' qabiley ka eik aadmi khada ho kar kehney laga : hamarey qabiley ki eik aurat Birwaa' binte Waashiq key barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aisa hi faisla farmaya tha. us aurat ney eik aadmi sey nikah kiya tha aur wo uskey sath sohbat karney sey pehley hi faut ho gaya tha. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke aurat ko us jaisi dusri aurton key mutabiq mehar milega. usey virasat bhi mileygi aur usey iddat bhi guzaarni hogi. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney (bator shukr aur khushi) apney haath uthaey aur Allahu-Akbar kaha. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke main nahin janta ke Zyada key ilawa kisi aur raawi ney is hadees mein Aswad ka zikr kiya ho."
3357,Hazrat Alqama sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey eik aurat key barey mein puchha gaya jis sey kisi aadmi ney nikah kiya aur wo mar gaya. abhi tak na to usney mehar muqarrar kiya tha aur na us sey jima (sambhog) hi kiya tha. wo log taqriban eik maah tak aatey rahey. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood unhen koi fatwaa nahin dey rahey they. aakhir-kar farmaya : mera khayal hai ke usey us jaisi aurton key mutabiq mehar milega. na kam na ziyada. usey (khawind sey) virasat bhi mileygi aur usey iddat bhi guzaarni hogi. to Hazrat Ma'qil bin Sanaan Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) ney gawahi di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Birwaa' bint Waashiq (Raziallahu anhu) key barey mein aap key faisley jaisa faisla farmaya tha.
3358,"Hazrat Masruq sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney us aadmi key barey mein jisney eik aurat sey nikah kiya aur mar gaya jab ke us ney na us sey jima (sambhog) kiya aur na us ka mehar hi muqarrar kiya, farmaya : aurat ko mehar ke jaisa milega. usey iddat guzaarni padeygi. usey virasat bhi mileygi. Hazrat Ma'qil bin Sanaan (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Birwaa' bint Vaashiq key barey mein aisa hi faisla farmatey suna hai."
3359,Hazrat Alqama ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey aisa hi waqia bayan kiya hai.
3360,"Hazrat Alqama sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key paas kuchh log aaye aur kehney lagey ke hum mein sey eik aadmi ney eik aurat sey shaadi ki, abhi us ney mehar muqarrar na kiya tha aur na us sey sohbat hi ki thi ke wo faut ho gaya. Hazrat Abdullah kehney lagey : jab sey main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey juda huwa hun, mujh sey is sey mushkil masla nahin puchha gaya. tum kisi aur key paas jaao. wo log eik maah tak uski baabat aap key paas aatey rahey. aakhir wo kehney lagey : agar hum aap sey na poochhen to aur kis sey poochhen? is shehar mein aap hi Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key azeem-qadr sahabi hain. aap key ilawa hamein koi aur shakhs nahin milta. aap farmaney lagey : main uskey mutalliq intehai soch bichaar sey fatwaa deta hun. agar sahih aur durust huwa to Allah Taala ki taraf sey hai jo akela hai aur uska koi shareek nahin. aur agar wo ghalat huwa to is mein kotahi meri hogi. aur kharabi shetan ki taraf sey. Allah Taala aur uska Rasool is sey bari hongey. mera khayal hai ke main uskey liye us jaisi aurton key mutabiq mehar muqarrar karun. na kam na ziyada. usey virasat bhi mileygi aur usey chaar maah das din iddat bhi guzaarni hogi. Ashja' qabiley key kuchh log bhi ye fatwaa sun rahey they. unhoney uth kar gawahi di ke bilashuba aap ney wohi faisla kiya hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamari eik aurat Birwaa' binte Washiq key mutalliq kiya tha. hamarey dekhney mein nahin aaya ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Islam key ilawa kisi aur baat par itney khush huye hon jitney us din khush huye (ke mera fatwaa hadeese-Rasool key mutabiq ho gaya)."
3361,"Hazrat Sahal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key yahan eik aurat aai aur kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney aap ko aap key sath nikah key liye pesh karti hun. wo kafi der khadi rahi. aakhir eik aadmi uth kar kehney laga : agar aap ko uski zarurat nahin to uska nikah mujh sey kar dijiye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : terey paas (mehar deney key liye) koi chiz hai. us ney kaha : merey paas kuchh nahin. aap ney farmaya : ja, talash kar agar-che lohey ki anguthi hi mil jaey. us ney talash kiya lekin usey kuchh na mila. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tujhey Quran Majeed ka kuchh hissa yad hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. falan falan sura yad hai. us ney chand Suraton ka tazkira kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey is Quran Majeed (ki taaleem) key iwaz jo tumhen yad hai, tera is sey nikah kar diya."
3362,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us aadmi key barey mein jo apni biwi ki laundi sey jima (sambhog) karta tha, farmaya : agar us (ki biwi) ney apni laundi ko uskey liye halal kiya tha to main usey sau kodey maaroonga aur agar us ney laundi ko uskey liye halal nahin kya tha to main usey rajm (sangsaar) karunga."
3363,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke eik aadmi jis ka naam Abdur-Rehman bin Hunain aur laqab Qurqura tha, ney apni biwi ki laundi sey jima (sambhog) kar liya. us shakhs ko (Makka ke governer) Hazrat Noman bin Bashir key paas pesh kiya gaya. unhoney farmaya : main iski baabat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wala faisla karunga ke agar us (teri biwi) ney us laundi ko terey liye halal kiya tha to tujhey kodey maaroonga aur agar us ney isey terey liye halal nahin kiya tha to tujhey pattharon sey (sangsaar) kar dunga. (tehqiq sey pata chala ke) uski biwi ney us laundi ko uskey liye halal kiya huwa tha, is liye sau kodey maarey gaey. Qatada ney kaha : mainey Habib bin Salim ko khat likha to unhoney mujhey ye hadees likh kar bheji."
3364,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi key barey mein jisney apni biwi ki laundi sey jima (sambhog) kar liya tha, farmaya : agar to uski biwi ney laundi ko uskey liye halal kiya tha to main usey sau kodey maaroonga aur agar us ney usey halal nahin kiya tha to main usey (sangsaar) karunga."
3365,"Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us aadmi key barey mein jisney apni biwi ki laundi sey jima (sabhog) kiya tha, faisla farmaya : agar us ney us sey zabardasti jima (sabhog) kiya hai to wo laundi (us key maal sey) azad ho jaeygi aur usey uski maalika ko us jaisi laundi deni hogi, aur agar laundi ki raza aur raghbat sey jima (sabhog) kiya hai to wo laundi uski ban jaeygi. albatta us mard ko us jaisi eik aur laundi biwi ko deni hogi."
3366,Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke eik aadmi ney apni biwi ki laundi sey jima (sabhog) kar liya. ye muqadma Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya. chunanche aap ney farmaya : agar us shakhs ney us sey jabran jima (sabhog) kiya hai to wo laundi uskey maal sey azad ho jaeygi aur khawind ko us jaisi laundi uski maalika (yani apni biwi) ko deni hogi aur agar wo razi aur khush thi to wo apni maalika ki raheygi. aur mard ko apney maal sey eik aur laundi biwi ko deni hogi.
3367,Muhammad ibne Hanifa (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye baat pahunchi ke eik aadmi mut'aa mein koi harj nahin samajhta. aap usey farmaney lagey : to to raahe-raast sey bhatka huwa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar (ki jang) key din mut'aa aur gharelu gadhon key gosht sey rok diya tha.
3368,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ghazwae-khaibar key din aurton key sath nikah mut'aa aur insanon key paas rehney waley gadhon ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya hai.
3369,Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar waley din aurton sey mut'aa karney sey mana farmaya. (raawi hadees) ibne Musannaa ney (khaibar waley din ki bajaey) Hunain wala din kaha (yani Hunain key din mana farmaya). aur ibne Musannaa ney kaha ke (ustaad) Abdul-Wahaab ney hamein apni kitab sey isi tarah hadees bayan ki.
3370,Hazrat Sabra Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke (eik dafa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mut'ey ki ijazat di to main aur eik doosra aadmi qabila banu Aamir ki eik aurat key paas gaey aur usey mut'ey ki pesh kaash! ki. wo kehney lagi : mujhey kya dogey? mainey kaha : apni chadar dunga. merey sathi ney bhi kaha : apni chadar dunga. merey sathi ki chadar meri chadar sey umda thi lekin main apney sathi sey ziyada jawan tha. jab wo merey sathi ki chadar dekhti to wo usey achchhaa lagta aur jab wo merey jism ko dekhti to main usey achchhaa lagta. bil-aakhir wo kehney lagi : to aur teri chadar merey liye theek hai. main uskey sath teen din raha. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs key paas is qism ki koi aurat ho jis sey wo mut'aa kar raha hai to usey chhod dey.
3371,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : halal aur haram nikah key darmiyan farq, daf bajaney aur aelane nikah karney ka hai."
3372,Hazrat Muhammad bin Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : halal aur haram nikah key darmiyan farq (aelane nikah ki) aawaz sey hota hai.
3373,"Hazrat Hasan Basri bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Aqeel bin Abi Talib ney banu Jasham ki eik aurat sey shaadi ki to unhen mubarak baad yun di gaee : tum mohabbat aur piyaar sey raho aur tumhen betey milen. Hazrat Hasan ney farmaya : uski bajaey is tarah kaho jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : (بَارَکَ اللّٰہُ فِیْکُمْ وَبَارَکَ لَکُم),''Allah taala tum mein aur tumharey liye barkat farmaey.''"
3374,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) key jism par safraa (khushbu) ka nishan dekha to farmaya : ye kya hai? unhoney kaha : mainey eik aurat sey soney ka sikka nawaah mehar muqarrar kar key shaadi ki hai. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala terey liye (is nikah mein) barkat farmaey. waleema zarur karna, chahey eik bakri key sath hi ho."
3375,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) aaye to un (key jism ya kapdon) par za'fraan key nishaanaat they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye kaisey? unhoney kaha : mainey shaadi ki hai. aap ney farmaya : kya mehar diya hai? unhoney kaha : soney ka sikka nawaah. aap ney farmaya : waleema bhi karna agar-che eik bakri hi ka ho.
3376,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) par safra (zard khushbu) ka nishan dekha to farmaya : ye kya hai? unhoney kaha : mainey eik Ansari aurat sey shaadi ki hai. aap ney farmaya : waleema karna, chahey eik bakri hi ka ho."
3377,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) sey nikah kiya to (kuchh dino key baad) mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Fatima ki merey ghar rukhsati farmaiye. aap ney farmaya : usey kuchh do, mainey kaha : merey paas to kuchh nahin. aap ney farmaya : teri hutami zireh kidhar gaee? mainey kaha : wo to merey paas hai. aap ney farmaya : wohi usey dey do."
3378,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) sey shaadi ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey kuchh do. unhoney kaha : merey paas to kuchh nahin. aap ney farmaya : teri hutami zireh kahan hai?
3379,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey shawwaal mein nikah farmaya aur shawwaal hi mein aap key yahan meri rukhsati hui. (bataao !) phir aap ki biwiyon mein sey kon aap key yahan mujh sey badh kar mohaboob hui?
3380,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey nikah farmaya to main chhe saal ki thi aur mujhey apney ghar abad farmaya to main nau saal ki thi aur gudiyon sey khelaa karti thi.
3381,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey nikah farmaya to main chhe saal ki thi aur mujhey apney ghar basaya to main nau saal ki thi.
3382,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khaibar ki ladaai key liye gaey. hamney subah ki namaz khaibar (ki basti) key qarib andherey (awwal waqt) main ada ki, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sawar huye aur Hazrat Abu-Talha bhi sawar huye, jabkey unkey peechhey main betha tha. khaibar ki galiyon mein Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni sawari ko tez kar diya. (sawari key daudtey waqt) mera ghutna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki raan mubarak sey chhu jata tha? (ke hawa ki wajeh sey aap ki raan sey chadar hat gaee) aur mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki raan mubarak ki safedi nazar aaney lagi. jab aap basti khaibar mein dakhil huye to aap ney (baa-aawaaze-buland) farmaya : Allahu-Akbar ! khaibar wiran huwa. bilashuba hum jab kisi qom key aangan mein padaaw kartey hain to un logon ki subah badi holnaak hoti hai jo (pehle se hi) aagah kiye gaey hon. aap ney teen dafa ye alfaz irshad farmaey. khaiber key log us waqt apney kaam kaaj key liye nikley. Abdul-Azeez ney kaha : khaibar waley kehney lagey : Muhammad (aa gaey) Abdul-Azeez ney kaha, aur hamarey baaz sathiyon key alfaz hain ke (khaibar walon ney kaha : ) Muhammad aur us ka lashkar aa gaya. (Hazrat Anas ney kaha : ) aur hamney khaibar bazor shamsheer fatah kiya, phir (qabzey mein aaney waley) qaidi ikhattey kiye gaey to dahiya (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Nabi ! mujhey in qaidiyon mein sey eik laundi ata farmaeyn. aap ney farmaya : jaao koi laundi ley lo. chunanche unhoney Safiya bint Hui ko ley liya, phir eik shakhs ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Nabi ! aap ney banu Qureza aur banu Nazeer dono qabeelon ki sardar Safiya binte Hui, dahiya ko dey di hai, halanke wo to aap key ilawa kisi key liye munasib nahin hai? aap ney farmaya : dahiya ko kaho, Safiya ko ley kar aaye. wo unhen ley aaye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen dekha aur farmaya : qaidiyon mein sey koi aur laundi ley lo. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Safiya ko azad farma kar un sey nikah farma liya. (Hazrat Anas key shagrid) Sabit ney puchha : Janab Abu-Hamza ! aap ney unhen mehar kya diya? unhoney farmaya : un ki jaan hi unka mehar thi. aap ney in ko azad kar diya aur un sey nikah farma liya yahan tak ke abhi raastey hi mein they ke (un ki iddat khatam ho gaee aur meri walida) Ummey Sulaim ney unhen banaya sanwaara aur raat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key khemey mein bhej diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey sath raat guzari. subah hui to aap ney farmaya : jis key paas khaney ki koi chiz hai, wo ley aaye. aap ney dasterkhaan bichhaney ka hukm diya. koi aadmi paneer lata tha, koi khajuren aur koi ghi. sahaba kiram ney sab chizon ko mila kar maleeda bana diya. aur ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka waleema ho gaya."
3383,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khaibar key raastey mein Hazrat Safiya binte Hui bin Akhtab key sath teen din (khususi taur par) thehrey jab aap ney unhen apney ghar basaya, phir Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) un aurton mein shamil thin jinhen pardey mein rakha jata tha."
3384,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khaibar aur Madina Munawra key darmiyan teen din Hazrat Safiya binte Hui (Raziallahu anhu) key sath thehrey shab-basri farmatey they. mainey musalmanon ko aap key waleemey ki dawat di. aap key is waleemey mein gosht tha na roti, balke aap ney dasterkhaan bichaney ka hukm diya aur is par kuchh khajuren, paneer aur ghi dala. ye aap ka waleema tha. musalman aapas mein kehney lagey ke ye aap ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) hain ya aap ki laundi? phir wo khud hi kehney lagey : agar aap ney unhen pardey mein rakha to phir wo Ummul-Mominin (yani aap ki zauja mohtarma (paak biwi)) hongi aur agar pardey mein na rakha to wo aap ki laundi hongi, phir jab aap ney safar shuru farmaya to (apni sawari par) apney peechhey unkey liye jagah tayyar ki aur unkey aur logon key darmiyan parda latka liya (taake log unhen na dekh saken)."
3385,"Hazrat Aamir bin Saad sey manqul hai ke main Qurza bin Kaab aur Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) key paas eik shaadi mein gaya to wahan bachchiyaan ga rahi thin. mainey kaha : aap dono Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Badri sahabi hain. aap ki mojudgi mein ye kuchh ho raha hai? wo kehney lagey : ji chahta hai to hamarey sath beth ja aur sun, nahin to ja. shaadi key moqe par hamein gaaney bajaney ki rukhsat (chhoot) di gaee hai."
3386,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( apni piyari beti) Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko eik chadar, eik mishkeeza aur eik sarhaana jis mein izkhir ki ghaas bhari hui thi, (rukhsati key moqey par) sath diye they."
3387,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik bistar aadmi key liye, doosra uski biwi key liye, teesra mehman key liye aur chotha shetan key liye."
3388,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : tu ney shaadi ki hai? mainey arz kiya : ji haan. farmaya : kya tumharey paas qaalin hain? mainey kaha : hamarey paas qaalin kahan? aap ney farmaya : yaqinan an-qarib tumharey paas qaalin hongey.
3389,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney shaadi ki aur apni zauja mohtarma ko ghar laye to meri walida Ummey Sulaim ney maleeda banaya. main wo ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya aur kaha : meri walida aap ko salam kehti hain aur kehti hain ke ye hamari taraf sey aap key liye maamuli sa tohfa hai. aap ney farmaya : rakh do. phir farmaya : jaao falan falan ko bula-laao balke jisey bhi milo (usey bula laao). aap ney kuchh logon key naam liye. jinkey aap ney naam liye they, main un sabko bula laya aur jisey bhi mila, usey bhi bula liya. (Hazrat Anas key shagrid ney kaha : ) mainey Hazrat Anas sey puchha : wo kitney they? unhoney kaha : taqriban teen sau afrad they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : das das aadmi halqa bana lein aur har shakhs apney qarib aur samney sey khaye. sab logon ney khana khaya yahan tak ke wo sair ho gaey. eik giroh jata raha, doosra aata raha. (jab sab farigh ho gaey to) aap ney farmaya : Anas ! uthaao. mainey bartan uthaya. main nahin janta ke jab mainey rakha tha us waqt ziyada tha ya jab uthaya, us waqt ziyada tha."
3390,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (hijrat key moqey par) Quraish (muhajrin) aur ansaar key darmiyan bhai chaara farmaya. aap ney Hazrat Saad bin Rabeea (Ansari) aur Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Muhaajir) Raziallahu anhuma ko aapas mein bhai bhai banaya. chunanche Hazrat Saad ney un sey kaha : merey paas jo bhi maal hai wo merey aur terey darmiyan mushtarak hai. meri do biwiyan hain, dekh jo tujhey achchhi lagey, main usey Talaq dey deta hun. jab iddat khatam ho to us sey nikah kar lena. Hazrat Abdur-Rehman ney kaha : Allah Taala terey ghar baar mein barkat farmaey. (main kuchh nahin lunga) mujhey bataao, tijaarati bazar kidhar hai? jab wapis aaye to wo (karobar key zariey sey) kuchh ghi aur paneer bacha laye they. Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ney kaha : (chand din baad) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh par safra khushbu key nishan dekhey to farmaya : ye kaisey? mainey arz kiya : mainey eik Ansari aurat sey shaadi kar li hai. aap ney farmaya : waleema karna chahey eik bakri hi ka ho."
